OL,3,CDeputy council leader fined #2,400
OL,4,Cover financial disclosure failings
OL,6,FA deputy council leader has been fined
OL,7,F#2,400 for failing to register a
OL,8,Ffinancial interest after lending a
OL,9,Ffriend #70,000 to part-fund a property
OL,10,Fpurchase.
OL,12,FTom Hollis, the deputy leader of
OL,13,FAshfield District Council in , was not
OL,14,Fdisqualified from serving as a
OL,15,Fcouncillor after a judge was told the
OL,16,F30-year-old had not acted dishonestly.
