OL,6,FShe also received #5,000 from another
OL,7,Fparty and bought a property in Forest
OL,8,FRoad, Skegby, for around #75,000.
OL,10,FHollis's barrister, Gul Nawaz Hussain
OL,11,FKC, told the court: "There was no
OL,12,Fdishonesty in this case and that's
OL,13,Fmost important when one considers the
OL,14,Frole that this man performs within his
OL,15,Flocal community."
OL,17,FHollis, of Yew Tree Drive, Huthwaite,
OL,18,Fnow has debts of around #80,000, said
OL,19,FMr Hussain, who told the court the
OL,20,Frationale behind the loan was to help
OL,21,Fa friend.
