OL,6,FPassing sentence, the Deputy Chief
OL,7,FMagistrate, Tan Ikram, said of Hollis:
OL,8,F"Throughout the period 2019 to 2021 he
OL,9,Fwas the beneficial owner of the said
OL,10,Fproperty and was re-elected twice
OL,11,Fwithout disclosure on his part of that
OL,12,Ffinancial interest.
OL,14,F"It is not suggested by the
OL,15,Fprosecution that the defendant was
OL,16,Fdishonest.
OL,18,F"It is not suggested that he
OL,19,Fbenefitted from any decision made in
OL,20,Fhis role as a councillor as regards
OL,21,Fhis non-disclosure.
