OL,6,F"These offences, I am told, only came
OL,7,Fto light because of a police inquiry
OL,8,Fin relation to an unrelated case, and
OL,9,Fbecause the matter was in the hands of
OL,10,Fthe police this matter comes before
OL,11,Fthe courts, rather than being dealt
OL,12,Fwith by internal processes within the
OL,13,Flocal authority."
